Fudge
========

Need to make some numbers look nicer? No worries, fudge them!

Example usage:

Fudge::round(67); # => 70
Fudge::round(117); # => 120
Fudge::round(472); # => 500
Fudge::round(7146); # => 7000

Fudge::price(67); # => 69.50 
Fudge::price(117); # => 119.00
Fudge::price(472); # => 495.00
Fudge::price(7146); # => 6950.00



